12 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
13 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
14 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 683.24a of Title 63, unless
15 there is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
16 A. The State of Oklahoma Office of Emergency Management shall
17 contract with a vendor to design and develop a statewide Stormwater
18 Management Predictive Analytic Solution. The Stormwater Management
19 Predictive Analytic Solution shall include an early warning
20 detection system and advanced flood monitoring solution. The
21 Stormwater Management Predictive Analytic Solution shall access and
22 visualize all relevant data; forecast future conditions; improve
23 forecasting models; provide real-time tracking and alerts, and
