2 management systems.
3 B. The Stormwater Management Predictive Analytic Solution shall
4 be operational no later than February 28, 2026. By March 31, 2026,
5 and annually thereafter, the Office of Emergency Management shall
6 submit a report to the Governor, Speaker of the Oklahoma House of
7 Representatives, and the President Pro Tempore of the Oklahoma State
8 Senate summarizing the information from the Stormwater Management
9 Predictive Analytic Solution and analyzing trends in that
10 information across years of data collection.
11 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2025.
